		</li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Other_palaces_and_structures">Other palaces and structures</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Persepolis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Other palaces and structures"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>The Council Hall, the Tryplion Hall, the Palaces of D, G, H, storerooms, stables and quarters, the unfinished gateway and a few miscellaneous structures at Persepolis are located near the south-east corner of the terrace, at the foot of the mountain.
</p>
<ul class="gallery mw-gallery-packed">
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 182.66666666667px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 180.66666666667px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Zoomorphic_Capital_(4679068036).jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Huma bird at Persepolis"><img alt="Huma bird at Persepolis" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Zoomorphic_Capital_%284679068036%29.jpg/271px-Zoomorphic_Capital_%284679068036%29.jpg" decoding="async" width="181" height="120" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Zoomorphic_Capital_%284679068036%29.jpg/407px-Zoomorphic_Capital_%284679068036%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/Zoomorphic_Capital_%284679068036%29.jpg/542px-Zoomorphic_Capital_%284679068036%29.jpg 2x" data-file-width="4288" data-file-height="2848" /></a></span></div>
			<div class="gallerytext"><a href="/wiki/Huma_bird" title="Huma bird">Huma bird</a> at Persepolis</div>
